## Object Spread

You can also spread object properties:

```javascript
const obj1 = { a: 1, b: 2 };
const obj2 = { c: 3, ...obj1 }; // { c: 3, a: 1, b: 2 }

// Useful for creating new objects without mutating the original
const updated = { ...obj1, b: 99 }; // { a: 1, b: 99 }
```

